{"tid":187371,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"刑罰學 - 監獄係為左懲教定係為左社教化","createTime":"2017-04-05T01:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T14:10:32.000Z","uid":74154,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d34e0c80c99a63591bbdfd8a4a01b930b12b1c","tid":187371,"uid":74154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T01:41:36.000Z","msg":"監獄有四個用途，其二就係懲罰同社教化，而依兩個特質會經常引起辯論。<br />\nFoucault講過'Not to punish less; to punish better, to insert power to punish more deeply into social body' 換言知，佢都係支持懲罰既，而懲罰亦都係對犯罪者犯法既報復。<br />\n直到18世紀尾，有人提出教化亦應成為監獄既其中一個目的，但係監獄其中一個目的就係係creating human suffering，咁一直受苦咁既人會唔會改過呢。<br />\n再者監獄既成效性係一直被質疑既，係依個情況下，大家覺得：<br />\n1. 監獄既目的應該係咩？<br />\n2. 監獄有否成功達成目的？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 監獄可否同時達到懲罰同社教化呢？</span>"},{"pid":"f3c52b07d9dc035ab8bb7122297779dc305eb5e7","tid":187371,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T01:43:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2759e791db3101b3427eaf89256b185df626031a","tid":187371,"uid":74154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T01:50:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>M男好想被S女調教<br />\n咁算係乜?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 差啲以為我禁錯標題<br />\nSM係雙向<br />\nM男應該算係..我唔知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995878b86fd03c42abf9e4510009b149f0f7f9ce","tid":187371,"uid":74154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T01:51:50.000Z","msg":"岩岩先睇到標題錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正確係監獄係為左懲<span style=\"color: red;\">罰</span>定係為左社教化先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6870d3610d64a606bb0104434276a74c100d25ae","tid":187371,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T01:53:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2222b0b0df5e3cdd0b364221b616e28a7252a74